{"tid":1162783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣辦事處遭噴油 何君堯「無面見人」","createTime":"2019-05-20T05:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T05:19:07.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eedb303b16982d127f142e0a67ba1a06f921ab90","tid":1162783,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LiFM9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LiFM9b.png&h=ac1e43fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZF3qYfS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZF3qYfS.png&h=2dbd2bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CGdB4VT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCGdB4VT.png&h=c149e9c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何君堯議員(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n位於荃豐中心2樓的何君堯立法會議員荃灣辦事處，被人噴漆油刑毀。中午12時左右，職員返回辦公，發現玻璃櫥窗遭人噴黑色油，何君堯的樣貌和印字也遭塗黑，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場正翻看商場閉路電視錄影調查，列刑事毀壞案處理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，辦事處運作3年，今次首次遭人破壞。"}]}